y Independent|The Offaly Independent]]'' (Owned by [[Celtic Media Group]] <ref name=\"westmeathexaminer.ie\"/>)\n* ''Tullamore Tribune'' (Owned by [[Iconic Newspapers]] <ref name=\"ReferenceC\"/>)\n\n====Roscommon====\n* ''[[Athlone Advertiser]]'' (Variant of Galway Advertiser). \n* ''Roscommon Herald'' (Owned by [[The Irish Times]] <ref name=\"irishexaminer.com\"/>)\n* ''Roscommon People''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.roscommonpeople.ie|title=Home \u2013 Roscommon People \u2013 The People's Paper|website=Roscommonpeople.ie|accessdate=25 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n====Sligo====\n* ''[[The Northwest Express (Newspaper)|The Northwest Express]]''\n* ''[[The Sligo Champion]]'' (Owned by [[Independent News and Media]] <ref name=\"independent.ie\"/>)\n* ''[[Sligo Weekender|Sligo Weekender]]'' (Owned by Dorothy Crean)\n\n====Tipperary====\n* ''[[Midland Tribune|The Midland Tribune]]''\n* ''[[The Nationalist (Tipperary)|The Nationalist]]'' (Owned by [[Iconic Newspapers]] <ref name=\"ccpc.ie\"/>) \n* ''[[The Nenagh Guardian]]''\n* ''[[Tipperary Star|The Tipperary Star]]'' (Owned by [[Iconic Newspapers]] <ref name=\"ccpc.ie\"/>)\n\n====Waterford====\n* ''The Dungarvan Leader''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dungarvanleader.com/|title=Dungarvan Leader Newspaper, Waterford, Ireland|website=Dungarvanleader.com|accessdate=25 August 2018}}</ref>\n* ''The Dungarvan Observer''\n* ''[[The Munster Express]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.munster-express.ie|title=Home|website=Munster-express.ie|accessdate=25 August 2018}}</ref>\n* ''[[Waterford News & Star]]'' (Owned by [[The Irish Times]] <ref name=\"irishexaminer.com\"/>)\n* ''Waterford Today''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.waterford-today.ie|title=Home|website=Waterford-today.ie|accessdate=25 August 2018}}</ref> (Free newspaper, owned by Voice Media <ref name=\"voicemedia.ie\"/>)\n\n====Westmeath====\n* ''[[Athlone Advertiser]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.advertiser.ie/athlone|title=Athlone News \u2013 Jobs, Property, Classifieds \